                     </h4>
                     <div class="expand_description">
                        <p>Accessibility metrics can extend the existing WCAG 2.0 conformance model to provide scores for the accessibility level of websites in more depth and detail. This Report provides considerations for validity, reliability, sensitivity, adequacy, and complexity as the main qualities of measuring web accessibility. The Report is a consolidated view of the outcomes of the <a href="http://www.w3.org/WAI/RD/2011/metrics/">Website Accessibility Metrics Online Symposium</a>.</p>
